description: Try our easy to follow Super-Green Frittata + Snacks recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Frittata,Pescatarian,Seafood free,Low salt,Blueberry,Egg,Low sugar,Halal,High protein,High fibre,Wheat free,Vegetarian,Spinach
name: SuperGreen Frittata + Snacks Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 180°C (160°C fanforced). Line 2 of the 2/3-cup-(160ml)-capacity muffin tin holes with paper cases.
Blanch broccoli in a saucepan of boiling water for 2 minutes or until tender. Refresh under cold running water, then drain. Coarsely chop.

Whisk the eggs and milk together in a medium bowl. Squeeze excess water from spinach. Stir through the spinach, broccoli and cheese. Ladle mixture into prepared muffin holes. Decorate tops of frittatas with thin slices of capsicum to make a face. Bake for 2025 minutes or until filling is set, puffed and golden.

Set aside to cool completely. Cover and store in fridge until ready to use. Snack 1: Yoghurt combined with blueberries Snack 2: Cruskits served with avocado (assemble at school) note: SuperGreen Frittata recipe serves 2
